"""
metrics_logger.py

Structured metrics logging for OpenVLA evaluation.
Supports logging episode-level and step-level metrics with full action smoothness tracking,
success/failure splits, and schema compatible with future token pruning integration.

Output files:
  - summary.json       : Overall experiment summary with all aggregates
  - episodes.jsonl    : Per-episode details (one JSON object per line)
  - episode_metrics.csv: Episode records in CSV format
  - step_metrics.csv  : Step records in CSV format (optional)
  - config.yaml       : Experiment configuration
"""

